{"tid":2261264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"麥美娟批網上眾籌「無王管」 政府：無意規管","createTime":"2020-10-28T07:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T11:55:07.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6382afe9247cd2b2c3530e28b6e6b48c6158877d","tid":2261264,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"政府指，目前沒有計劃擴展規管籌款活動的法例至網上眾籌。有議員批評，政府無意堵塞相關法例漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n財經事務及庫務局局長許正宇：「有關法例的立法原意，是為了防止在公眾地方進行相關籌款活動時，會造成妨擾或者阻礙，相關法例不適用在網上籌款活動，現階段無計劃把相關法例延伸到網上籌款活動。洗錢那些活動，其實已經有規管，作為規管角度，不一定每一個環節都要有角色。」<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員（新界西）麥美娟：「局長知否月初有一個人聲稱籌得1600萬，但之後又說要解散，錢不知道去那，繼續這樣拿錢。用眾籌的方式，不用交稅、不用牌照，又不用報告，比出糧更好。局長你們的工作到底是怎樣？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/._u1UTpBM0C041Azu.U1iA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/L-FUND-201028-13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F._u1UTpBM0C041Azu.U1iA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FL-FUND-201028-13.jpg&h=c1c8b33f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6a7df074f34014d0fc45b23ad78a6f3cf64d8ab","tid":2261264,"uid":252318,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T07:33:54.000Z","msg":"我鐘意俾錢人洗關你閪事咩"},{"pid":"694dd574424702726c853cdd0428856420c5f9cb","tid":2261264,"uid":121197,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T07:49:36.000Z","msg":"眾籌平台本身都會留意會唔會有不尋常嘅大筆錢資助架on9"},{"pid":"7407ee0b9ce0f8919b0b5b40bf38d3f0467283ee","tid":2261264,"uid":256246,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T07:50:31.000Z","msg":"mayanne係咪又想爆粗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa222b2d688c76f12a0dcb2a53afaa000724742b","tid":2261264,"uid":32588,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T07:56:24.000Z","msg":"係都規管咗幾千萬一幅字畫的籌款晚會先啦<br />